commitResults.messageTitle: Refactor CSS Structure: Separate Color and Layout Styles
commitResults.messageBody:
- Moved all color-related styles to DarkTheme.css to centralize color configuration.
- Moved all UI layout and sizing-related styles (e.g., padding, font sizes, borders) to Extensions.css for better separation of concerns.
- Added LightTheme.css to provide an alternative color scheme for light-themed UI.
- Ensured all UI elements follow the new structure for color and layout styling.
